Salvador Dalí was a prominent Spanish surrealist painter born in Figueres, Catalonia, Spain.
Dalí was a skilled draftsman, best known for the striking and bizarre images in his surrealist work. His painterly skills are often attributed to the influence of Renaissance masters.  His best-known work, The Persistence of Memory, was completed in August 1931. Dalí's expansive artistic repertoire included film, sculpture, and photography, in collaboration with a range of artists in a variety of media.

Product name: SNES- Earthbound
Description:
UPDATE ON SHIPPING! PLEASE READ!
All Cartridge games and cases from 8/20/16 on,  will be shipped in a box to prevent damage to the games or case. This added a small increase in shipping cost but will help insure your items get to you as the left Retro Gamer and Backups.
The GAME DOES BOOT UP AND PLAY ALL THE WAY THROUGH WITH NO PROBLEMS. NO PROTECTION LOCKS
All games are custom made with all new boards, chips and labels . These are not imports from China. With todays technology they are made even stronger than the originals and may even be heavier than the originals.
Works on the Retron 5 and Original SNES hardware! 
EarthBound features many traditional role-playing game elements: the player controls a party of characters who travel through the game's two-dimensional world composed of villages, cities, caves, and dungeons. Along the way, the player fights battles against enemies and the party receives experience points for victories.  If enough experience points are acquired, a character's level will increase. This increases the character's attributes, such as offense, defense, and the maximum hit points (HP) and psychic points (PP) of each character. Rather than using an overworld map screen like most console RPGs of its era, the world is entirely seamless, with no differentiation between towns and the outside world. Another non-traditional element is the perspective used for the world. The game uses oblique projection, while most 2D RPGs use a "top down" view on a grid or an isometric perspective.
Unlike its predecessor, EarthBound does not use random encounters. When physical contact occurs between a character and an enemy, the screen dissolves into battle mode. In combat, characters and enemies possess a certain amount of HP. Blows to an enemy reduce the amount of HP. Once an enemy's HP reach zero, that enemy is defeated. If a specific type of enemy is defeated, there is a chance that the character will receive an item after the battle. In battle, the player is allowed to choose specific actions for their characters. These actions can include attacking, healing, spying (reveals enemy weakness/strengths), mirroring (emulate a specific enemy), and running away. Characters can also use special PSI attacks that require PP. Once each character is assigned a command, the characters and enemies perform their actions in a set order, determined by character speed. Whenever a character receives damage, the HP box gradually "rolls" down, similar to an odometer. This allows players an opportunity to heal the character or win the battle before the counter hits zero, after which the character is knocked unconscious.[b] If all characters are rendered unconscious, the game transitions to an endgame screen, asking if the player wants to continue. An affirmative response brings Ness, conscious, back to the last telephone he saved from, with half the money on his person at the time of his defeat, and with other party members showing as still unconscious. Because battles are not random, tactical advantages can be gained. If the player physically contacts an enemy from behind (indicated by a translucent green swirl which fills the screen), the player is given a first-strike priority. However, this also applies to enemies, who can also engage the party from behind (in this case, the swirl is red). Neutral priority is indicated by a gray swirl. Additionally, as Ness and his friends become stronger, battles with weaker enemies are eventually won automatically, forgoing the battle sequence, and weaker monsters will begin to flee from Ness and his friends rather than chase them.
Currency is indirectly received from Ness' father, who can also save the game's progress. Each time the party wins a battle, Ness' father deposits money in an account that can be withdrawn at ATMs. In towns, players can visit various stores where weapons, armor, and items can be bought. Weapons and armor can be equipped to increase character strength and defense, respectively. In addition, items can be used for a number of purposes, such as healing. Towns also contain several other useful facilities such as hospitals where players can be healed for a fee

Product name: OFF WHITE wedding garter set, customizable, bridal garter, lace garter, keepsake and toss garter, wedding garter, flower garter, Monogram
Description:
♦ DESCRIPTION
This high quality, off white wedding garter set features a keepsake garter with a unique floral Alencon lace applique (3 3/4" x 7 3/4") embellished with elegant glass pearls. A soft stretch lace trim is carefully sewn on with off white thread by hand. Then, layers of soft ivory tulle are hand sewn unto the back of the lace applique for comfort and to enhance the overall color. 
The tossing garter is included and has a small lace applique (2" x 3 1/4") embellished with one glass pearl. The stretch lace used in the first picture is sold out, but the one used in the second picture is available and measures 7/8" in width. All stretch lace choices are soft, comfortable, and stretchy.
You can choose the color of the pearls. Please leave me a note when you checkout as to which color you would like, or if you would like rhinestones instead of pearls, or if you prefer plain lace without anything on it.
(The available pearl colors are white/off white, light ivory, ivory, nude, champagne, golden champagne, peach, toffee, gold, copper, brownish silver, silver, pewter, pink off white, light pink, peachy pink, medium pink, hot pink, dark rosy mauve, raspberry/wine, red, orange, lime green, mint green, sage green, old willow, forest green, teal, turquoise, light blue, aqua, dark aqua, navy blue, antique blue, purple, light purple. Please see picture 5.)
The whole set includes:
- Keepsake Garter
- Tossing Garter
- White Gift Box
- Safety Pins
- Hollywood Fashion Tape 
*Please remember to use the fashion tape included in the box even if the garters fit perfectly at first because due to the force of gravity, things like to travel down especially as the leg becomes thinner going down. You can use it just for the keepsake garter, or chop it in half and use it for both garters. :)
*** The invoice will not be included in the package unless you request it to. So if you are purchasing a gift, or just want to save paper, I got you covered. ***
♦ CONSTRUCTION STYLE
  (see picture 3)
- Style A) both garters are NOT backed with any tulle
- Style B) both garters are backed with layers of soft ivory tulle. 
- Style C) construction style A with the addition of one monogram
- Style D) construction style B with the addition of one monogram
- Style E) construction style A with the addition of two monograms
- Style F) construction style B with the addition of two monograms
In the past, all of my Alencon lace garters sets were made with style B construction. The price difference is due to the amount of time it takes me to carefully sew and trim the tulle. I recommend getting style B because without the tulle, the back of the Alencon lace applique is a little uncomfortable and gritty. Also, the tulle makes the whole garter set have a nice warm, off white color. If your skin is very sensitive, I also offer crushed tulle which feels like soft cotton. Style A is perfect for those who have tight budgets, don't mind the discomfort, or are planning to sew on their own backing. 
The monogram is machine embroidered with special embroidery thread. You may choose to have your own custom monogram on the keepsake garter, tossing garter, or both garters. You may also choose what color you would like the embroidery to be in. 
♦ SIZE (PLEASE READ!!!!!!!!!!)
I will need your thigh measurement/circumference (aka. size) in order to make your garter set fit perfectly. To measure your thigh:
1)	Please pick a place where you plan to wear the keepsake garter (preferably 4 inches above the knee)
2)	Wrap a soft tape measure around your thigh. Round your measurement to the nearest ½ inch.
3)	Please give me your exact measurement, and DO NOT TAKE ANY INCHES OFF. 
I will take a few inches off of the measurement you give me to make sure the fit is just right. The tossing garter will be made a few inches smaller than the keepsake garter because it will be worn a few inches below. 
♦ STRETCH LACE BAND STYLE
PLEASE leave me a note when you checkout about which stretch lace band style you would like me to make your garter set with (see picture 4). If you don't leave me a note, I will be using style #2. 
♦ PRODUCTION TIME
As of now, most orders are finished and shipped within 7 days. I will be using USPS first class mail, which takes 2 to 5 days to reach your residence. So if you need it in the next 1 to 3 days, please send me a conversation, and we will need to upgrade your shipping.
♦ LASTLY...
If you like this design, please view the rest of my designs here: 
https://www.etsy.com/shop/BridalByCrysteliz.
 
If you have any questions or requests about anything, please do not hesitate to send me a conversation through the Etsy system. I really appreciate each and every order you place with me, and I promise you great customer service, high quality designs, affordable prices, and a 10% off coupon with every purchase! Thank you so much for viewing my design and I hope you have a blessed day! :D

This is a beautiful custom sized bridal garter set handmade with ivory stretch lace, clear crystal rhinestones in silver color settings and pearl beading. These garters are stunning! The larger one is 2" wide and the smaller one is approximately 1.5" wide.
The best thing about my garters is that they are NO SLIP! On my wedding day I wore a garter that was very similar to the ones in this set.  I loved the design but I can't tell you how many times my garter fell off, and it was annoying to say the least when I had to keep stopping and signalling for my sister to come and help me slide it back up my leg (I couldn't exactly bend over in my ribbing lined and fitted wedding dress). When my husband and I made our escape to the car after the recept my garter fell off in the parking lot as we were running and I never found it. This inspired me to come up with beautiful garters that won't fall off.  All of these garters are lined with a silicone strip on the inside to prevent slipping.
It is important that you leave a note when you checkout so I know the exact size to make your garter.  With the custom fit and the no slip grip you will love these awesome garters.

Product name: Eyeglass Holder, Colorful Beaded Eyeglass Chain, Millefiori Reading Glasses Lanyard,  Fun Chain for Glasses
Description:
This is a colorful Millefiori Eyeglass Chain that is full of fun and detail!  It's a wonderful accessory in that it matches any color, yet looks amazing with black and white as well.  This entire chain is approximately 30 inches long.
Millefiori beads are so special because their color penetrates throughout the entire bead.  They are not painted or surface, they are made from colored glass canes that are layered.  So the gorgeous colors are vibrant throughout!
Wear your glasses in style using this very unique, fun, and simple eyeglass chain.  It is useful and convenient and also makes a wonderful gift!
*Please note:  The bead colors and order will vary from chain to chain.  Due to the handmade nature of these beads, no two will be exactly alike.
